track_notes: This is the shortest path to this summit; by car the road is very small to reach the parking. the walk is easy on a large forest road and a small path at the end; from the top you can see the other sota all around and the sea too; also available repeater R3 and R6 + Dstar digipeater + DMR
track_title: Short walk to Cime du Castel

track_notes: This summit is not really my favorite, but the village Blausasc is a nice place, nothing to see, may be one church. You have to found out witch track will do for you. Need some water in summertime.
Just for fun and to remember that summit witch is no more listed! This path is very short!
